&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Design Draughtsperson plays a crucial role in our engineering team, contributing to the creation of detailed design drawings and technical documentation using SolidWorks and Vault. The primary objective is to support the product development process by transforming conceptual designs into accurate, comprehensive drafts. This role involves collaborating with cross-functional teams to ensure the seamless translation of ideas into practical and manufacturable solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
