&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Technical Documentation:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate comprehensive technical documentation, including bills of materials (BOMs) and assembly instructions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure that all drawings and documents are in compliance with relevant codes and standards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Collaboration:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with engineers and other stakeholders to understand design requirements and specifications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Participate in design reviews and provide input to enhance the overall quality of designs&lt;/li&gt;
