&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conduct thorough reviews of own work to identify and rectify errors or discrepancies.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the implementation of quality control measures within the drafting process.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Continuous Improvement:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay abreast of industry trends and advancements in design software.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Contribute to process improvement initiatives to enhance the efficiency and effectiveness of the drafting team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
