&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Position Summary&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Document Control Clerk is responsible for managing and maintaining the documentation system to ensure compliance with industry standards and company procedures. The ideal candidate will have strong organizational skills, attention to detail, and experience in document management within a manufacturing environment.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Minimum Qualifications&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
