&lt;p&gt;We support customers operating in environments where failure is not an option. Our products support aerospace, defense, and space applications that demand exceptional workmanship, process control, and attention to detail. If you are passionate about developing manufacturing processes, building robust test systems, and helping launch high-reliability products, we would like to talk&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;with you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About 603 Manufacturing&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
