&lt;p&gt;Through a comprehensive understanding of both brands, their customers, markets, and capabilities, this position creates a customer-first environment in which employees, processes, workflows, tools, and systems can be deployed to create sustainable profitable growth and value for shareholders through our engineered solutions and technical applications.&lt;/p&gt;
